snippet.title: Supreme Sprinter trailer
snippet.description:
Coming to Android in January 2020!


Zoom your way through this new infinite runner environment, using different sports balls. Based on a prototype from a university project, Supreme Sprinter is the newest infinite runner which allows you to speed through a tropical environment as footballs, basketballs, snooker balls and more!
